The paper focuses on natural language processing (NLP) techniques to extract product functionality information from questions. This falls under the scope of computational linguistics (cs.CL). The use of semi-supervised learning and neural networks also suggests relevance to information retrieval (cs.IR), machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and deep learning (cs.DL).
